          <p>
            Books appointments directly into your PMS in real-time, eliminating back-and-forth and reducing scheduling friction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="capability-card">
          <div class="capability-icon">
            <i class="ti ti-message-circle-question"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Answers Common Questions</h3>
          <p>
            Provides instant, accurate answers to patient questions about services, pricing, insurance, location, and hours.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="capability-card">
          <div class="capability-icon">
            <i class="ti ti-user-check"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Smart Lead Qualification</h3>
          <p>
            Qualifies leads based on your custom criteria including treatment interest, financial capability, and urgency level.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="capability-card">
          <div class="capability-icon">
            <i class="ti ti-bell-ringing"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Confirmations & Reminders</h3>
          <p>
            Automatically sends appointment confirmations and reminders via SMS and voice to reduce no-shows by up to 80%.
