      <div class="demo-icon">
        <i class="ti ti-microphone"></i>
      </div>
      <h2>Talk to Maria, Our AI Receptionist</h2>
      <p>
        Experience our AI voice technology firsthand. Click below to have Maria reach out to you 
        via text or call—just like she does for your potential patients.
      </p>
      <a href="/book-a-call" class="demo-cta-button">
