            Your team gains over 10 hours per week by eliminating repetitive phone tasks. They can 
            focus on delivering exceptional in-person patient care instead of being tied to the phone 
            all day.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-badge">
            <i class="ti ti-rocket"></i>
            Speed Wins
          </div>
          <h3>Instant Response = Higher Conversion</h3>
          <p>
            Studies show that responding to leads within 5 minutes increases conversion by 400%. 
            Our AI responds in seconds, every single time—ensuring you book more appointments 
            than practices that rely on callbacks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-badge">
            <i class="ti ti-shield-check"></i>
            Quality Assured
          </div>
